location.fullValue: Ash Plan, The Hills at Lorson Ranch

data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of Lorson Ranch! Walking distance to schools, parks, trails, and an easy commute to Colorado Springs, Ft. Carson, Peterson AFB, Schriever and Cheyenne Mt! This Dawson model by Saint Aubyn is very unique to the neighborhood. Very few neighbors will have this vaulted ceiling floorplan with loft and finished basement. It's the perfect layout! This four-bedroom, four-bath residence offers wonderful views and privacy, backing to open space. Upon entry, you'll be greeted by a foyer accompanied by an open floorplan with impressive vaulted ceilings. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living space, dining and kitchen, allowing for flow and a sense of spaciousness throughout. Main floor powder room for convenience. The heart of the home is the living area that is open to the kitchen and has a walk-out to the concrete patio and spacious, level yard. Great for entertaining! The kitchen is a delight, equipped with stainless Whirlpool appliances, ample counter space, large pantry, coffee bar and ample storage. In addition, this home features a light and bright dining room with vaulted ceilings, great for gatherings. One of the attributes of this floorplan is the MAIN FLOOR PRIMARY SUITE! Unwind in the spa-like soaking tub, walk-in shower, dual vanities, and large walk-in closet. Upstairs you'll be delighted to find a loft area, perfect for your home office, library or gaming center. Two bedrooms upstairs are generously sized, ensuring comfort and privacy for family members or guests. Another unique feature of this home is the two guest rooms are joined by a Jack-n Jill bath. Wait until you see the finished basement with HUGE family room and large windows for additional light. The 4th oversized bedroom and full bath are located in the basement retreat. Perfect for teens, out of town guests, or home gym. Storage galore! Easy access to shopping, I25, and Colorado Springs Airport. NO HOA! Make this your home today!
